node.text:
It's the most crazy time to be alive & celebrating a birthday! It's a bitter sweet day for me & for us all. I woke up this morning to the rain & so deeply sad, and only a few minutes later the sun is now shining and it's going to be a beautiful day. 
I realize this birthday is about the world coming together as one rainbow, believing in all colors & countries to unite as one and hold strong together. We will all have our pot of gold at the end... we will dance in the streets together again, we will raise our glasses to the sky with tears of joys in our eyes and laugh and sing and hug and kiss together again! But today... I do it alone, with you all in my heart and tears falling down my face right now in deep sadness. I am heartbroken, I can't lie about this. 
But I believe there is a light at the end of the tunnel, like the one that shines through my window this very moment, it's giving me all the hope right now. 
We will rise, we will hold each other & fly... TOGETHER... we will be again. I miss you my friends and wish nothing more then to be able to celebrate this special day with my loved ones. 😔 
Happy St Patrick's Day everyone.🍀🌈⭐️ Thank you for giving me the best decade of my life and supporting me through this last epic dance around the sun. It's been the best years ever, I look at everything moving forward as extra bonus points. I've lived the best life I could have ever dreamed of and I am forever grateful. 💚  #thisis40 #birthdaygirl #luckycharm  #shamrock #birthdayapocolypse #isolatedbirthday #beleiveinthepoweroflove

node.text: We will do many things in our life and never get recognition for it. We will challenge ourselves to greatness others simply dream of. We will fail time and time again with the risks we take and no one will be able to pull us out of the darkness to meet the light other than our own selves. Most people will live wild & magical lives that should be published in books and never will even receive a thank you note for the imprint of amazing they left behind during their time here... So why do we all do it? Why do we keep on keeping on when we might not even get a high five for a life full of blood, sweat, passion and tears? Because, it's only the eyes in the mirror that matter and if you don't believe in yourself and love who you are... Then life ain't worth a damn and who the hell are you doing it all for? BELIEVE IN YOU... Your light of life comes from within, no one shines it better than you! So.... Be sure to leave a trail of your epicness for the world to see when it's good and ready. ~QUIET WARRIOR~ #lovelife #laurenlife #beyourownhero #quietwarrior #seabambassador #seabaheli #ooscclothing #yniqeyewear #bataleonsnowboards #capranea #auclairgloves #hainesalaska

node.text: Last night I was sitting at dinner in Santa Monica with 7 amazing friends of mine. Every one of them I have met on a mountain, at a different time in my life while shredding🏂⛷. Not one person had I met at the same time or place, but it was... on a an epic mountain on an epic day. And here we were... all together, eating fish tacos and drinking margaritas on a beautiful Sunday evening in June. Telling stories of powder days & our deep passion of #shredlife.
